NAME
    App::lcpan::Daemon - Daemon-mode lcpan

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.050 of App::lcpan::Daemon (from Perl
    distribution App-lcpan-Daemon), released on 2020-05-08.

SYNOPSIS
    See lcpand-simple script for the Riap::Simple server.

    See "www/lcpand.psgi" in this distribution's share files for the PSGI
    application.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/App-lcpan-Daemon>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-App-lcpan-Daemon>.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests on the bugtracker website
    <https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=App-lcpan-Daemon>

    When submitting a bug or request, please include a test-file or a patch
    to an existing test-file that illustrates the bug or desired feature.

SEE ALSO
    App::lcpan

